realtimeweb.businesssearch.regular

Class SearchResponse

  • Object
    • realtimeweb.businesssearch.regular.SearchResponse

  • public class SearchResponse
extends Object
    A SearchResponse is returned by a search of businesses around a Location. It has a list of businesses, a suggested region of a map to display those businesses, and the total number of businesses found by the search (which will often be more than the list of businesses in the SearchResponse, since usually only the first 20 results are returned). In order to access these extra businesses, use the offsetResults or paginate filters in the BusinessQuery.
    Author:
    acbart
